<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>: (التَّفْنُ) ،<span class="c5"> بالفتحِ:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>أَهْمَلَهُ الجَوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَهُوَ <span class="c2">(الوَسَخُ)</span> .<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
